Vancouver Canucks Defeat Boston Bruins 1-0, Lead Stanley Cup Final 3-2

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-06-11T02:56:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-11/vancouver-canucks-defeat-boston-bruins-1-0-lead-stanley-cup-final-3-2.html
Maxim Lapierre scored early in the
third period and Roberto Luongo recorded his second shutout of
the series as the  Vancouver Canucks  beat the  Boston  Bruins 1-0
to take a three-games-to-two lead in the Stanley Cup Final.  Game 6 in the best-of-seven series is scheduled for June 13
in Boston. If the Bruins win that game, Game 7 will be back in
 Vancouver  on June 15.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  